Token.Abstract: This protocol ensures that the object that is added in the priority queue has a comparisson mechanism.
Returns an NSComparisonResult value that indicates the ordering between to given objects.

Parameter.Name: obj1
Parameter.Abstract: The first object for the comparison

Parameter.Name: obj2
Parameter.Abstract: The second object for the comparison

ReturnValue.Abstract: NSComparisonResult constant which is used to indicate the order.
